# DOCS_TEST: example_001

query error
SELECT title, year, rating
FROM movies
WHERE rating > 8.0
ORDER BY rating DESC
LIMIT 10;
----
db error: ERROR: Table with name movies does not exist!
Did you mean "<slt:ignore>"?


